{"tid":2224511,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［免費永遠係最貴] 小王子攝影 伏","createTime":"2020-09-30T14:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T15:03:30.000Z","uid":298946,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a0b12d6bd65a4fe1458d3d85f0736617cbb68b31","tid":2224511,"uid":298946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T14:13:26.000Z","msg":"喺佢嗰度買咗畢業袍，跟住話免費送你去影樓影相（但要交左100蚊留位費先）。<br />\n本身都唔想去，但屋企人好似好想去咁咪去囉。<br />\n<br />\n事前已經知道包五張免費相，同埋一個相框。終於到咗去嗰日，一去到就叫你拍片，乜撚野畢業感想。我心諗，都唔撚包，係咪跟住又係咁sell我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住即刻上網睇吓，先知道中左伏。即走。"},{"pid":"5e44247a3b7aeea34eccfabd027b6e7d452c80aa","tid":2224511,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:06:02.000Z","msg":"即走？<br />\n好7喎即走"},{"pid":"5978a618cbca82e62541feaba56da70fdb127f6d","tid":2224511,"uid":144833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"見佢長期請人 有冇做過嘅講吓"},{"pid":"250c975ce22aeabd6e949e40e8610a51fbf4b54d","tid":2224511,"uid":345381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T05:26:02.000Z","msg":"定力夠就可以攞返1舊水、1個實體相架同5張相既softcopy 走人"},{"pid":"4910276db1c3f3e1144b5659300c740bd0ce47d3","tid":2224511,"uid":185410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5978a618cbca82e62541feaba56da70fdb127f6d","tid":2224511,"uid":144833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T15:07:03.000Z","msg":"見佢長期請人 有冇做過嘅講吓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T05:20:47.000Z","msg":"八千請你做學徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97fb4a359013788513f07b4aa2691ffd6e47987","tid":2224511,"uid":144833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4910276db1c3f3e1144b5659300c740bd0ce47d3","tid":2224511,"uid":185410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5978a618cbca82e